Review and validate this AI-generated workout plan. Your tasks:
1. Ensure the JSON structure is exactly correct with all required fields
2. Verify exercise selections are appropriate for the user profile
3. Ensure sets/reps/rest are realistic and safe
4. Fix any formatting issues

User Profile:
