  "days": [
    {
      "day": "Day A",
      "focus": "string",
      "exercises": [
        { "name": "string", "sets": number, "reps": "string", "rest": "string", "notes": "string or empty string" }
      ]
    },
    { "day": "Day B", ... },
    { "day": "Day C", ... }
  ],
  "tips": ["string", "string", "string"]
}

Ensure exactly 3 days. Each day must have 5-6 exercises. sets must be a number, reps must be a string like '8-12'. rest must be a string like '60s'.

